   "source": [
    "# AI-Powered PII Discovery → Human Review → Tag → Auto-Mask\n",
    "\n",
    "An **AI-assisted** flow for keeping the PII target list current as the JSON evolves:\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    " ai_query classify  →  confidence score  →  HUMAN REVIEW GATE  →  apply governed tag  →  ABAC auto-masks\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "An LLM proposes PII labels with a confidence score, findings are **reviewed by a human before\n",
    "enforcement** (here, via an approval table), and only *approved* labels drive governance. Once a\n",
    "column is tagged, the **schema-level ABAC policy** from `pii_masking_json_demo` masks it\n",
    "automatically — no per-table change.\n",
    "\n",
    "> Treat AI output as a **starting point**. Nothing is enforced until a human approves it."
   ]
  },
