    "`pii_masking_json_demo` notebook reads) and merge in the discovered leaf keys, and (c) apply the governed\n",
    "tag to the JSON column. The schema-level ABAC policy created in `pii_masking_json_demo` then masks the\n",
    "column automatically. If the discovered keys extend the config, update `config/pii_policies.json` and\n",
    "re-run §5 of `pii_masking_json_demo`."
